## 7. Traceability and Handoff

### 7.1 Traceability Matrix

| Driver ID | Objective ID | BR ID | SR / TR ID | Downstream FR / NFR ID |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| DR-001 | OBJ-001 | BR-001 | SR-001 | [To be completed in FR / NFR templates] |

### 7.2 FR / NFR Handoff Notes

- Functional details, system behavior, process steps, screen behavior, validations, integrations, and acceptance criteria must be captured in the FR template.
- Performance, security, availability, scalability, auditability, usability, accessibility, localization, observability, and supportability requirements must be captured in the NFR template.
- Each FR and NFR should trace back to one or more BR IDs from this BRD.

